Available Tools: list_commits | get_commit | create_branch | delete_branch | list_branches | compare_branches
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "owner": "string", "repo": "string", "branch": "string", "sha": "string" }
Response Schema: { "commits": [{ "sha": "string", "message": "string", "author": "string", "date": "string" }], "branch": "string" }
---
Question: Show me the last few commits on the main branch of the acme-corp/backend-api repository.
Call: { "func_call": "list_commits", "owner": "acme-corp", "repo": "backend-api", "branch": "main", "sha": "" }
Response: { "commits": [{ "sha": "a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345678901234567890abcd", "message": "feat: add user authentication middleware", "author": "Alice Johnson", "date": "2023-10-25T14:30:00Z" }, { "sha": "b2c3d4e5f6789012345678901234567890abcdef", "message": "fix: resolve database connection timeout", "author": "Bob Smith", "date": "2023-10-24T09:15:00Z" }, { "sha": "c3d4e5f6789012345678901234567890abcdef12", "message": "chore: update dependencies to latest versions", "author": "Charlie Brown", "date": "2023-10-23T16:45:00Z" }], "branch": "main" }

